window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>My name is Danica James. I'm a cop with the Arcane Division.</p> <p>Most mages have the ability to manipulate the elements - fire, water, air, earth, electricity. My magic only works on machines and electrical devices. They call me a magitek. That doesn't help much with demons and vampires, let alone criminals with lethal magikal powers.</p> <p><b>Contains mature themes.</b></p>"; 
